{"tid":1850683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭有病","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T20:25:16.000Z","uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d33d88e0cc3156daccc35e9d9192894c6a7b1f2a","tid":1850683,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FY0yiTQk7ww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFY0yiTQk7ww&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=5257594e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FY0yiTQk7ww</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fCWnJ0LkLM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfCWnJ0LkLM4&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=c4d7ff35\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fCWnJ0LkLM4</a><br />\n<br />\n頂自己有病就唔好拖香港人去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黐鬼線做吓精神鑑定好喎<br />\n<br />\n搵個痴線婆香港唔死先奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 好心睇下醫生啦<br />\n成日覺得被迫害唔好放棄治療啦, <br />\n連最簡單嘅因果關係都唔識,<br />\n輕重都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸都唔夠口罩仲話問大陸攞口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span styl